INSERT INTO `wp_rg_lead_detail` VALUES (1,1,1,1,'test'),(2,1,1,2,'test@gmail.com'),(3,1,1,3,'test'),(4,2,1,1,'test'),(5,2,1,2,'test@test.com'),(6,2,1,3,'asfd'),(7,3,1,1,'test'),(8,3,1,2,'test@test.com'),(9,3,1,3,'sd'),(10,5,1,1,'Don Pelham'),(11,5,1,2,'dapelham@yahoo.com'),(12,5,1,3,'TEST\r\n\r\nHi Eric,\r\n\r\nDidn\'t know if this had been tested yet. \r\n\r\nThis is just a TEST. :)'),(13,6,1,1,'steve kramer'),(14,6,1,2,'steve.kramer@legalmatch.com'),(15,6,1,3,'Eric\r\nLet me know whether the following snap shot of some of our recent financially capable Dallas-Fort Worth Metro Area commercial litigation clients looks like a fit.\r\n\r\nCordially,\r\n\r\nSteve Kramer\r\nFor Legal Match\r\n310-990-3026 \r\n\r\n\r\nCase Details\r\nCase ID:	C168909840471\r\nDate posted:	03/29/2016\r\nExpiration date:	05/13/2016\r\nStatus:	Active\r\n	\r\nAnticipated method(s) of payment include:	Check \r\nLegal assistance needed in:	Irving Texas 75063 \r\nDALLAS County\r\nLegal categories:	Breach of Contract\r\nCase Summary\r\nLent money to a gym owner to help grow his busines\r\nI lent $50,000 to a gym owner to help grow his business with a promise note (notarized). He also formed an LLC and made me 30% partner with promise to share profit every month. But so far I have not received a single dime let alone the profit sharing.\r\nAdditional Information by Category\r\nBREACH OF CONTRACT\r\nThe contract was entered into on this date:\r\n11/01/2015\r\nThe contract was:\r\nWritten, and I have a copy\r\nThe approximate $ value of the contract is:\r\n$: 70000\r\nThe contract was breached on this date or over this time period:\r\n11/15/2015\r\nThe approximate $ value that I stand to lose or have lost because of the breach of contract is:\r\n$: 50000\r\nThe likelihood that I will be able to collect money from the other party if I win is:\r\nGood\r\n\r\n\r\nCase Details\r\nCase ID:	C168172756381\r\nDate posted:	03/21/2016\r\nExpiration date:	05/05/2016\r\nStatus:	Active\r\nLawyer experience leve